OL,3,CMan charged with murder after death of
OL,4,Ca woman in Cardiff
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of a woman at a
OL,8,Fhouse on Caerphilly Road in Cardiff
OL,9,Fwhich was reported in the early hours
OL,10,Fof Tuesday, 20 August.
OL,12,FAlcwyn Thomas, 44, from the Heath area
OL,13,Fof Cardiff, has been charged with
OL,14,Fmurder and is scheduled to appear
OL,15,Fbefore Cardiff Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,FFriday, 23 August 23.
OL,18,FThe victim has been named as Victoria
OL,19,F'Vicki' Thomas, 45, from Caerphilly
OL,20,FRoad in Cardiff.
