OL,6,FVicki's family has released the
OL,7,Ffollowing statement: "As a family we
OL,8,Fare devastated that our much-loved
OL,9,Fdaughter, mother, sister, aunt, niece
OL,10,Fand friend has been taken away so
OL,11,Ftragically.
OL,13,F"Our family are broken, and we will
OL,14,Fmiss her forever. Please respect our
OL,15,Fprivacy and our wishes to grieve at
OL,16,Fthis devastating and difficult time."
