OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Matt Powell,
OL,7,Ffrom South Wales Police, said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts are with Vicki's family who
OL,9,Fcontinue to be updated and supported
OL,10,Fby family liaison officers.
OL,12,F"As our investigative work continues
